  "description": "Variation of condition 1 (Plans Numbers) and removal of condition 18 (Layout) pursuant to planning permission 17/5180/FUL dated 15/02/18 for `Ground floor rear extension to extend existing retail shop. Conversion of upper floor levels into 10no. self-contained flats including first floor rear extension, extension to roof involving raising ridge height 1no rear dormer with 2no juliet balconies and terrace, balcony to second floor front elevation and 7no. front rooflights. Associated refuse/recycling facilities and 11no. off-street parking spaces. New vehicular access from Falkland Avenue including electronic gates. Erection of single storey office building to rear.`  Amendments include increase in electricity substation size, one additional parking space directly off Falkland Avenue, replacing the previously proposed bin store. Alterations to entrance points and retail unit. Insertion of louvres to the bike shed and fire escape. Pitched roof design on the southern and northern elevation to the rear of the site have been removed and the second floor extended,  increasing the size of flats 7 and 8, balcony 1 and 2, and terrace 3.  Internal changes to flat 6 including moving one of the bedrooms to the southern edge of the site.  Changes to the rear communal hallways configuration and alterations to the roof pitch, creation of glass balustrades to roof",
